TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Effect of Consumer Experience on Brand Loyalty and the Structure of Market Demand
AU  - Demsetz, Harold
AB  - [This paper deals with the subject of brand loyalty. It contains statistical tests for the presence of a learning function that leads buyers to purchase in a manner reflecting greater reliance on personal experience and less reliance on seller advertising efforts.]
