TY  - JOUR
TI  - Identification and Estimation in a Simultaneous Equations Model with Errors in the Variables
AU  - Konijn, H. S.
AB  - [Problems of simultaneous equations were first examined in connection with errors-in-variables models, but formal results on identification were published only for the errors-in-equations model. This paper shows that very similar results hold for the errors-in-variables cases. It also examines limited information, maximum likelihood estimation for this case.]
